HEADWORD: Scrawl
<hw>Scrawl</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>See
<er>Crawl</er>.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Latimer.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
